{
  "texts": [
    "Imagine at the end of a public elective course you are taking, the teacher grades each student with a final score consisting of everyone's daily class performance and a final exam.",
    "However, you are discontented with your score and have some questions.",
    "Is the score given by the teacher fair?",
    "Is the marking process transparent?",
    "Why did I get this score?"
  ]
}